About the Developer

Hi, I'm Umair Khan

Frontend Developer | React Specialist

Welcome to QuranHub! I'm a passionate developer who loves creating meaningful web applications that combine modern technology with purposeful design.

This project was developed as part of my assessment for the Quran team, where I aimed to create an intuitive and emotionally intelligent way for people to connect with the Holy Quran through technology.

I specialize in building responsive React applications with clean, maintainable code. My goal is always to create experiences that are both beautiful and functional.

What I Built

📚 Smart Surah Recommendations

AI-powered emotional detection to suggest relevant Quran chapters based on user's feelings

⚡ React + TypeScript

Modern, type-safe development with smooth animations and responsive design

🎨 Clean UI/UX

Beautiful, accessible interface that focuses on user experience and simplicity

Let's Connect

Feel free to check out my work and reach out if you'd like to collaborate!
